242
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,600
and then bend our knees.

243
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:39,600
Lean our upper body towards the ball

244
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:41,300
and place our weight on our left foot.

245
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:42,400
Then, for the grip,

246
00:14:42,400 --> 00:14:46,100
