247
00:14:46,100 --> 00:14:48,400
Lift the club horizontally.

248
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:50,000
Keep your head still.

249
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,500
Correct.

250
00:14:52,700 --> 00:14:54,800
Tilt the club, then go down.

251
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:56,700
Hit the ball horizontally.

252
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:57,900
Lift the club.

253
00:14:57,900 --> 00:14:59,500
Eyes to the front.

254
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:01,000
Backswing.

255
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:02,800
Try it.

256
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:04,400
Okay.

257
